Account Deletion Instructions

Last updated: September 6, 2025

How to delete your account

To delete your account from the Airsmile game, please follow these quick steps:

  1. Open your email app and start a new message to oleksii.zonov@gmail.com.
  2. Set the subject line to “Delete account.”
  3. In the message body, specify which account you want to delete (e.g., your nickname or user ID).
  4. Attach a screenshot showing you are signed in to Google so we can verify ownership.
  5. Send the email. We will process your request and confirm the deletion.
Tip: Be sure the screenshot clearly shows your Google account name/email while logged in.
